{"word":"προσάγω","slug":"προσάγω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>προσάγω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρός\">πρός</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄγω\">ἄγω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘bring to/forward’, of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> or place, <b>bring <a href='B:470 18:24'>Mt 18:24</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:490 9:41'>Lk 9:41</a>; <a href='B:510 12:6'>Ac 12:6</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:510 16:20'>16:20</a>;</b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> sense <b><a href='B:670 3:18'>1 Pt 3:18</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘move toward’, <b>approach,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fr.\">fr.</a> the perspective of the sailor, who is actually the one drawing near with his ship <b><a href='B:510 27:27'>Ac 27:27</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:προσαγορεύω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:προσαγωγή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}